re access\n- [[id:c66dcb2a-7b86-11f0-9347-938641e9519d][Node Red]]\n\n** Automations\n- Camera events → MQTT → Frigate recording triggers\n- Garage door opener (Shelly 1 relay + reed switch) integration\n- Presence detection via VLAN/device state\n- Voice assistant experimentation (local LLMs + TTS/STT)\n\n** Usage\n- Central control for smart home devices\n- Integration hub between IoT hardware, cameras, and Kubernetes-hosted services\n- Testing ground for advanced automations (voice, AI, n8n workflows)\n\n** Notes\n- Frigate detection is disabled; HA relies on MQTT events for efficiency\n- Certificates managed via OPNsense + HAProxy (HTTP disabled once HTTPS available)\n- VMs are low-traffic; CPU overcommitment on Proxmox is acceptable\n', 'properties': {'embedding': '0.406776 1.115247 -3.111906 -0.128874 0.247930 -0.876756 -0.165258 0.102561 1.215844 -1.098527 -0.680048 0.934269 1.068659 0.653508 -0.167065 -0.241101 0.110237 1.037355 -0.997037 -0.741328 0.502527 -0.763643 -1.462386 -0.262190 1.757310 1.155311 -0.415199 -0.168708 0.164882 -0.156414 0.484660 -0.600746 -0.706870 -0.372598 -0.633763 -0.271606 1.306801 0.077270 -0.877417 0.826855 -0.064656 -0.993157 0.153047 -0.885128 0.262482 0.496845 0.306285 -0.291578 0.699705 -0.473427 0.017284 -0.147098 -0.003095 0.015866 1.812817 -0.700700 -0.047177 0.894448 -0.115453 -0.446955 1.274114 0.952630 -0.082703 2.319088 1.158894 0.300656 -0.127557 0.843372 -0.358318 0.358929 -0.606427 -1.072034 0.470031 0.559981 -0.223315 0.405054 -0.114904 -1.131059 -0.287754 0.452963 0.635463 -0.435946 1.629001 -0.652192 0.707702 -0.344374 -0.673814 0.252268 -1.228117 0.996556 0.527503 1.023485 -0.666234 -0.230804 -0.949131 -0.004963 -0.079676 -0.260644 -0.371282 -0.880835 -0.768166 -0.121535 0.219947 -0.011363 0.622440 1.212875 -0.919833 0.409873 -0.348595 0.255954 -0.057512 0.412593 -0.629700 -0.797556 0.404102 -0.623410 2.268662 -0.362808 0.278225 0.588506 -0.345170 -0.513181 -0.039004 0.465331 -0.000965 0.259730 -1.868906 0.5627