e in the 9th or 10th grade\n- Upgraded to a Commodore 64 in 11th or 12th grade\n\nUSAF:\nEnlisted on April 15, 1988\n- Basic training in San Antonio, TX\n- Tech school at Lowry AFB, Aurora, CO\nB-1B Offensive Avionics technician at McConnell AFB, KS\n- Promoted to Senior Airman below the zone\n- Promoted to Staff Sergeant on 2nd attempt\n\n- B-2 flight test Program, Edwards AFB, CA 1992\n- Completed Computer Science Bachelor's degree from Chapman University\n\n- Separated in September, 1998\n\n- Began working as a software developer at BDS/Tallan immediately after separating from USAF\n- Built a powerful home lab and infrastructure for learning, creating, and contributing\n\n", 'properties': {'embedding': '0.537352 0.985393 -3.701222 -0.990677 -0.178919 0.673028 0.805981 -0.213300 0.982995 -0.803598 -0.910794 0.153807 0.626999 1.563988 0.123694 -1.250655 -0.730074 -0.567291 -0.761458 -0.205155 0.035909 -1.774879 0.043538 -0.042411 1.663862 0.514398 -1.713125 -0.970576 -2.163699 -0.030503 0.946948 -0.361962 -0.689158 -0.062172 -1.017041 -0.086902 0.000097 0.635623 0.094736 -0.148867 1.611916 -0.156797 -0.785321 -1.374812 -0.106239 0.076350 0.323683 -0.430736 0.814775 0.037922 0.296420 0.321632 0.134345 0.068286 0.545632 -0.741310 0.292847 0.278509 0.088293 0.647638 2.304320 1.870211 -0.680743 0.913522 0.419852 -0.138990 0.220500 1.350649 -1.094281 -0.214250 0.409290 -1.338776 -0.526131 0.319192 -0.696618 1.056091 -0.331411 0.092953 -0.070844 1.052819 0.697446 0.013025 0.098009 -0.456051 0.430985 -0.262732 0.078678 -0.342699 -1.690109 1.564205 0.083138 1.824403 -0.389982 0.866309 0.011063 0.058163 0.071486 -0.579150 -0.097410 -0.444072 -0.498409 -1.801991 0.845879 0.143243 1.293665 0.872989 0.315969 -1.033032 0.017533 -0.026834 -1.105643 0.304531 -0.974286 -0.890846 0.834279 0.345809 0.026202 -0.334174 -0.207340 0.381987 -0.823089 -0.745907 -0.518888 0.212543 -0.124667 0.221560 -0.601930 -0.044834 -0.274602 -0.493858 -0.449859 -0.819843 0.017605 0.633839 0.177544 0.25