24 -0.420763 -0.487959 0.235482 0.031351 0.102049 0.249744 0.199747 0.374582 -0.710427 -0.549871 0.754027 0.049468 -0.493802 0.142416 -0.007688 0.316181 0.594820 0.280617 0.584742 -0.134193 0.327367 0.001656 -0.351556 0.227733 -0.142974 -0.180066 0.348380 -0.292166 -0.225424 -0.605487 0.839847 0.209869 -1.105937 -0.171980 0.703646 0.149866 0.333329 -1.088822 -0.065607 -0.159673 -0.429983 0.568987 -0.672560 -0.323702 -0.257169 -0.223844 -0.682260 -0.497334 0.782906 0.026903 -0.708720 -0.518982 0.116013 -1.046493 -0.344293 0.015766 0.074368 -0.502613 0.106421 0.458072 -0.225676 0.334639 1.221318 -0.009670 -0.219192 -0.325314 -0.371718 -0.196001 0.394396 -0.607057 -0.001165 -0.060784 0.475994 1.578549 0.602804 1.023988 -0.392352 0.590256 0.136290 -0.655707 -0.497194 -0.620735 0.135761\n:END:\n\n#+title: n8n Automation Platform\n\n** Overview\nWorkflow automation and AI orchestration service running in ProxMox LXC container. Serves as the primary automation hub for knowledge management workflows and Matrix chat integration.\n\n** Infrastructure Details\n- **Platform:** ProxMox LXC Container #121\n- **OS:** Linux (Debian-based)\n- **Network:** Management VLAN\n- **Storage:** ZFS shared storage mounted at ~/mnt/org-roam~\n- **Access:** Web interface + API endpoints\n\n** Service Configuration\n- **n8n Version:** Latest stable\n- **Installation:** Docker-based deployment\n- **Database:** SQLite (local workflow storage)\n- **Webhook Endpoint:** ~d58e25ad-79f7-4d89-aad3-b9af05f6444f~\n- **External Access:** Reverse proxy via Caddy\n\n** Integrated Components\n*** Doom Emacs + Org-Roam\n- **Purpose:** Knowledge base backend for AI workflows\n- **Config Location:** ~/root/.config/doom/~\n- **Database:** Org-roam SQLite database\n- **API Functions:** ~enhanced-notes-api.el~ for n8n integration\n- **Daemon:** Emacs server for emacsclient API calls\n\n*** Ollama AI Platform\n- **Purpose:** Local LLM inference for workflow processing\n- **Model:** gpt-oss:20b for intent classification and response generation\n- **Integration:** LangChain nodes in n8n workflows\n- **Performance:** Handles multiple concurrent AI agent requests\n\n** Primary Workflows\n- [[id:1755213300][Org-Roam AI Workflow]]\n\n** Network Integration\n- **Domain:** Part of ~cruver.network~ infrastructure\n- **Matrix Integration:** Receives webhooks from Element/Matrix servers\n- **API Endpoints:** RESTful webhooks for external service integration\n- **Monitoring:** Health checks and workflow status reporting\n\n** Storage Architecture\n- **Shared Storage:** ~/external-storage/org-roam~ (ZFS dataset)\n- **Mount Point:** ~/mnt/org-roam~ within container\n- **Sync Strategy:** Syncthing replication to personal devices\n- **Backup:** Included in ZFS snapshot strategy\n\n** Service Dependencies\nThe n8n service implements automation workflows that depend on several infrastructure components:\n\n*** Core Dependencies\n- **Ollama LXC:** Provides AI inference for workflow intelligence\n- **Matrix Server:** Receives chat messages and delivers responses\n- **ZFS Storage:** Persistent storage for org-roam knowledge base\n- **Caddy Reverse Proxy:** External access and SSL termination\n\n*** Integration Points\n- **Prometheus Monitoring:** Workflow execution metrics and health status\n- **Matrix Notifications:** Alert delivery for workflow failures\n- **Backup System:** Automated backups of workflow configurations\n\n** Operational Notes\n- **Startup Dependencies:** Requires Ollama and shared storage to be available\n- **Resource Usage:** Memory scales with concurrent AI processing requests\n- **Maintenance:** Workflow updates deployed via n8n web interface\n- **Monitoring:** Built-in execution logs and error tracking\n\n** Security Configuration\n- **Network Access:** Restricted to management VLAN and authorized external endpoints\n- **Authentication:** n8n admin interface secured with credentials\n- **API Security:** Webhook endpoints use secure random identifiers\n- **Container Isolation:** ProxMox LXC provides process and filesystem isolation\n\n** Performance Characteristics\n- **AI Processing:** Sub-second response times for intent classification\n- **Search Performance:** Org-roam database queries typically <100ms\n- **Workflow Execution:** End-to-end chat response average 2-3 seconds\n- **Concurrent Capacity:** Handles multiple simultaneous Matrix conversations\n\n** Troubleshooting & Maintenance\n*** Common Issues\n- **Emacs Daemon Restart:** ~pkill -f "emacs.*daemon" && emacs --daemon~\n- **Database Sync:** Force org-roam sync via ~(org-roam-db-sync \'force)~\n- **Workflow Debugging:** n8n execution logs show detailed error traces\n- **Memory Management:** Container restart clears any memory leaks\n\n*** Monitoring Points\n- **Container Health:** ProxMox resource monitoring\n- **Service Status:** n8n web interface health dashboard\n- **AI Processing:** Ollama response times and error rates\n- **Storage Access:** ZFS mount status and available space\n\n** Related Infrastructure\n:PROPERTIES:\n:ID:       dc68f1d8-53d1-4d52-82c9-bfc0a1ea1302\n:EMBEDDING: -0.283091 1.205305 -3.236664 -0.439494 1.458401 -0.880373 0.864349 -0.216344 0.235084 -0.714009 0.078406 -0.473403 0.945391 0.377684 0.284595 -0.113365 -0.345721 0.057371 0.040704 -0.813794 0.068638 -0.709480 0.028309 -0.335095 1.974757 0.491319 -0.479150 -0.094984 0.218107 0.331272 1.170184 0.212723 0.260963 0.168206 -0.612994 -1.255681 0.772782 -0.092371 0.349796 0.513686 -0.291251 -0.498339 -0.348287 -0.985825 0.859998 0.645106 -0.011226 -0.886710 0.653846 -0.540882 0.559138 0.266000 0.297118 1.075700 1.515443 -0.088764 -0.281262 0.758757 -0.547994 -0.752607 1.513591 1.870132 -0.163502 0.707258 1.109221 0.466419 -0.533103 0.235613 -0.505925 -0.099736 0.523913 0.318582 0.147377 0.596806 0.555624 0.965014 -0.099978 -0.624813 -0.584544 1.403748 0.777847 -0.565958 0.744213 -0.721714 0.849444 0.428543 -0.674710 -0.304831 -0.108555 2.107803 -0.143298 0.214700 -0.211255 -0.162108 -0.484274 0.49167