erver)\n- **Type:** LXC container\n- **Networking:** IoT VLAN, accessible internally via `nodered.cruver.network`\n- **Access:** Web UI over HTTPS (proxied through OPNsense/HAProxy)\n\n** Automations\n1. **Sprinkler Control**\n   - Automates irrigation schedules and manual control\n   - Interfaces with smart relays/valves\n\n2. **Garage Door Safety**\n   - Monitors Shelly 1 relay + reed switch state\n   - Closes garage door automatically if left open for extended periods\n\n3. **Frigate Recording Triggers**\n   - Listens for camera motion/person events via MQTT (amcrest2mqtt)\n   - Sends start/stop re\n*ERROR*: Unknown message: -p\n*ERROR*: Unknown message: rint-nonl cording&_signals&_to&_Frigate\n\n**&_Integrations\n&-&_**Home&_Assistant**&_(event&_orchestration&_+&_dashboard&_control)\n&-&_**MQTT&_(HiveMQ&_broker)**&_for&_device&_and&_camera&_events\n&-&_**Frigate**&_for&_NVR&_functionality\n&-&_**Shelly&_1&_relay&_+&_reed&_switch**&_for&_garage&_door&_integration\n\n**&_Usage\n&-&_Offloads&_automation&_logic&_from&_Home&_Assistant\n&-&_Provides&_visual&_flow&_programming&_environment\n&-&_Enables&_complex&_multi&-service&_workflows&_with&_low&_overhead\n\n**&_Notes\n&-&_Lightweight&_containerized&_deployment&_(LXC)&_on&_Proxmox\n&-&_Integrated&_with&_ZeroTier&_indirectly&_through&_OPNsense\n&-&_Flows&_backed&_up&_to&_Git&_(recommended&_for&_version&_control)\n', 'properties': {'embedding': '0.426387&_1.492196&_&-2.852514&_&-1.150266&_0.704327&_&-1.688768&_&-0.340395&_&-0.299903&_0.279466&_&-1.097107&_&-0.060005&_1.069515&_1.109744&_0.567728&_0.390694&_&-0.090126&_&-0.019665&_0.565293&_&-0.223608&_&-0.680790&_0.029898&_&-0.138300&_&-1.20\n0956 -0.161139 1.439861 1.243563 -0.346083 -0.311588 -0.150778 -0.457007 0.392157 -0.775597 -1.103801 -0.457718 0.012613 -0.646595 0.552427 -0.048323 -0.057895 1.174092 0.219411 -0.375201 0.290464 -1.456816 -0.035825 0.180482 0.851565 -0.007947 0.759218 -0.909888 0.414447 0.093782 -0.744351 0.379385 1.089009 0.066693 0.628718 1.1